## 4. Actian VectorAI Collections Schema

| # | Collection Name | Dimension | Written By | Queried By | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `document_chunks` | 384 | Doc Agent | CAM Agent, Risk Agent | Chunked PDF paragraphs for semantic evidence retrieval |
| 2 | `financial_profiles` | 384 | Doc Agent | Risk Agent, Bias Agent, Model Selector | Vectorized financial snapshots for similar-case lookup |
| 3 | `gst_patterns` | 384 | GST Agent | GST Agent, Monitor Agent | Embedded GST summaries for fraud pattern matching |
| 4 | `bank_recon_profiles` | 384 | Bank Recon Agent | Risk Agent, Monitor Agent | Reconciliation pattern fingerprints |
| 5 | `news_articles` | 384 | Web Agent (seed) | Web Agent | **Replaces Weaviate `NewsArticle`** |
| 6 | `litigation_records` | 384 | Web Agent (seed) | Web Agent | **Replaces Weaviate `LitigationRecord`** |
| 7 | `rbi_circulars` | 384 | Web Agent (seed) | Web Agent | **Replaces Weaviate `RBICircular`** |
| 8 | `mca_filings` | 384 | MCA Agent | MCA Agent | **Replaces Weaviate `MCAFiling`** |
| 9 | `pan_profiles` | 384 | PAN Agent | PAN Agent, Compliance Agent | Cross-application PAN dedup |
| 10 | `risk_decisions` | 384 | Risk Agent | Risk Agent, Bias Agent, CAM Agent | Similar past application outcomes |
| 11 | `pd_transcripts` | 384 | PD Agent | PD Agent, CAM Agent | Interview pattern matching |
| 12 | `stress_scenarios` | 384 | Stress Agent | Stress Agent, CAM Agent | Historical stress survivability |
| 13 | `audit_events` | 384 | Monitor Agent | Monitor Agent | Anomaly detection in processing patterns |
| 14 | `application_summaries` | 384 | CAM Agent | All agents | Full application context for cross-app intelligence |

